      <div class="flo-block-text-block-2 flo-block-text-block-2--835">
    <div class="flo-block-text-block-2__text-content"><p>Our first chance to photograph this stylish couple was in a drive around photo session which included their favorite Atlanta skyline viewpoint. I love the exciting energy between this bride and groom which was clearly evident in their photographs especially they were near each other,</p>
<p>One of our favorite venues in Buckhead is the secluded and historic Estate and its lush and secluded property. Tony Conway and his Legendary Events team are always terrific at creating lovely weddings and this event was no exception.</p>
<p>The couple’s facial expressions tell the happy story of this wedding celebration from preparations to the ceremony and on to their dinner reception. It was a day filled with laughter, dancing, and festive celebration. For us, it was an idyllic assignment with plenty of visual cues that always make for exceptional storytelling.</p>
</div>
